  "texts": [
    "It is an approach that identifies named entities in text using predefined set of rules.",
    "Rules are generated with the help of language experts.",
    "These rules are created patterns and grammatical structures associated with named entities like name of persons, organization, location and dates.",
    "Rules-based systems can be effective in specific domains or languages where patterns are defined clearly, but they might struggle with handling variations and evolving language usage.",
    "Anandika et at."
  ]
